ygData.messageBody:
My teleport Prob is over. I'm back on good ol'
Antonica (even though I love Faydwer). I wish that that
tele "Stonehenge" place was a little closer to FP, in
a safer zone than West Commons. Maybe EC. Anywho,
I'm kinda angry that Round Kick replaces Kick and
isn't seperate. I guess its more realistic this way
(how would you be able to kick then round kick in a
row but not kick twice?). I just was hoping to have
some cool combos going like in Fighting Games. Left,
Right, Low Kick, Slide, Uppercut, K.O.<br><br>That would
look so cool.<br><br>Thanks, I'm gonna reinstall soon.
